# Stripe Payment Link URL (developer-only)
#
# 1. Stripe Dashboard → Product catalog → Payment links → + Create
# 2. Choose one-time payment; enable "Customers choose what to pay" for tips
# 3. Copy the link (https://buy.stripe.com/... or https://donate.stripe.com/...)
# 4. Paste into js/01-constants.js → SUPPORT_STRIPE_PAYMENT_URL
# 5. Rebuild: node scripts/package-extension.mjs
#
# Example (replace with your link):
# https://buy.stripe.com/xxxxxxxx
